docs/context/architecture-brief.md:224:## 14. STACK-ADR-001 技术栈与架构检查
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:226:本节是 `STACK-ADR-001` 的落盘约束，用于后续脚手架、实现和验证任务统一对齐。当前阶段只定义独立微服务技术栈、目录边界和架构检查入口，不创建业务实现。
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:232:- HTTP 框架: Fastify
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:233:- MySQL 客户端: Kysely + `mysql2`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:234:- Migration 工具: Kysely Migrator 或等价 TypeScript migration runner
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:241:- `src/server.ts`: HTTP server entry
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:242:- `src/workers/scheduler-worker.ts`: scheduler worker entry
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:243:- `src/jobs/cleanup-job.ts`: cleanup job entry
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:244:- `src/config/`: 配置加载入口
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:248:`STACK-ADR-001` 的目标目录必须显式包含以下路径，后续实现和测试任务应按这些路径拆分 owned paths：
