docs/context/architecture-brief.md:274:- 标准命令: `npm run arch:check`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:279:1. `src/server.ts`、`src/workers/scheduler-worker.ts`、`src/jobs/cleanup-job.ts` 存在。
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:280:2. `contracts/openapi.yaml` 的公开 operation 可以映射到 `src/routes/` 下的 route/handler 与测试清单。
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:290:### 14.6 后续 owned_paths 约束
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:292:`STACK-ADR-001` 后续实现任务应拆成具体模块路径，不应只写笼统目录名。建议拆分方向如下：
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:294:- API 相关：`src/routes/`、`src/task-api/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:295:- 注册配置相关：`src/registry-config/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:296:- 调度相关：`src/scheduler/`、`src/workers/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:297:- 查询相关：`src/query-executor/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:298:- 文件相关：`src/file-service/`、`src/jobs/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:299:- 审计相关：`src/audit-log/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:300:- 数据访问相关：`src/repositories/`、`src/db/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:301:- 测试相关：`tests/contract/`、`tests/api/`、`tests/db/`、`tests/worker/`、`tests/query/`、`tests/file/`、`tests/sample/`
docs/context/architecture-brief.md:303:当前 `task.json` 中的 `SERVICE-SCAFFOLD-001` 仍含笼统 `tests/` 边界；由于本轮强制边界不修改 `task.json`，下一次由 `harness-writer` 或 `planner` 处理计划时，应把它拆成 `tests/contract/`、`tests/api/`、`tests/worker/` 等具体路径，再进入后续实现任务。
